TY  - JOUR
T1  - Note—A Branch-and-Bound Approach to the Bicriterion Scheduling Problem Involving Total Flowtime and Range of Lateness
AU  - Sen, Tapan
AU  - Raiszadeh, Farhad M. E.
AU  - Dileepan, Parthasarati
Y1  - 1988/02/01
PY  - 1988
